note: Saresh Babita Group (SBG) is a consolidated firm of its diverse enterprises. It was found in 2018 with an aim to affiliate and deliver its different products with one business name. Its foremost inception dates back to 1995 when the present-day Chairman of SB Group and the Executive Director of Everest Group, Mr. Saresh Kumar Saraff ventured sugar manufacturing and distribution in Nepal.
